{"tid":2356462,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"人生第一次成年之後半夜賴尿","createTime":"2021-01-06T22:41:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T08:26:58.000Z","uid":345289,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"9963317aa0edc2876818f31d6b4e25f684c5620d","tid":2356462,"uid":345289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T22:41:41.000Z","msg":"頭先發左幾個惡夢 然後醒左 <br />\n去廁所發現全條底褲濕晒<br />\n以為自己係出汗<br />\n<br />\n點知返房發現連張床單都濕埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係平時半夜急尿識起身去<br />\n第一次賴尿<br />\n好驚身體出現問題<br />\n定係因為呢排工作壓力大<br />\n發完惡夢所以咁樣...<br />\n但係夢入面無去廁所嘅畫面<br />\n自己都完全無印象有去廁所嘅感覺<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（認真POST"},{"pid":"33d489661a1fab624293ff573f7b1917cf05b345","tid":2356462,"uid":249708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T22:43:50.000Z","msg":"[img]圖片網址[/img]？"},{"pid":"34da0986db879cc7a6778a66d07eef2ca67426fd","tid":2356462,"uid":345289,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"33d489661a1fab624293ff573f7b1917cf05b345","tid":2356462,"uid":249708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T22:43:50.000Z","msg":"[img]圖片網址[/img]？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T22:46:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e1a442993c695fe194a11182b4eb3997b960974","tid":2356462,"uid":131522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T22:51:47.000Z","msg":"瞓之前飲咗水？"},{"pid":"9c4f65b8cc6ce4eb35052c6e96a7bdd44b1e2067","tid":2356462,"uid":81309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T22:52:25.000Z","msg":"似係壓力 <br />\n有咩唔開心講低"},{"pid":"24031e8560c69c3fdfea7d202676aa4c46f0efe1","tid":2356462,"uid":196625,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T22:55:39.000Z","msg":"你工作壓力太大<br />\n太攰啦。<br />\n所以一放鬆就全身放鬆<br />\n咁咪瀨<br />\n<br />\n大警號黎<br />\n唔好咁辛苦啦<br />\n<br />\n我自己都試過。<br />\n另外睇我連登名"},{"pi